      <para styleclass="Heading1">Mechanism | Add Trace-Point</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2">Add Trace-Point</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">What is a Trace-Point?</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">A <text styleclass="Element">Trace-Point</text> shows the locus of a moving <text styleclass="Element">Point</text> for one machine-cycle on the <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Plane</text> of the active <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-Trace-Point" anchor="DragaTrace-Point">Special Conditions</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">: to drag the </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">, to help you find a </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT">good</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Element">Trace-point.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_">Add Trace-Point</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="7" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:103px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName" style="text-align:right;"><image src="MD-Icon-AddTracePoint.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"><title>Add Trace-Point</title></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; height:26px;">
