        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Notes">Note</text>: &#160;<text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Trace-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> does </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="color:#ff0000;">not</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> add a </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to the model - you must select a </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text styleclass="Element" style="font-size:14pt; color:#000000;">*</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> that is in the model. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text style="font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold;">*</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Interface">start-Point</text>, <text styleclass="Interface">end-Point</text>, <text styleclass="Interface">center-Point</text>, or <text styleclass="Element">Point</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:103px;">
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="VariableName">What to do : </text></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; color:#003300;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="Body Text">Do </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Trace-Point</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics" styleclass="T_Menu">Kinematics FB toolbar</link><text styleclass="VariableName"> &gt; </text><text styleclass="T_Menu">Add Trace-Point</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click a </text><text styleclass="Element">Point</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> in the model and </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">If the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Select-Elements" styleclass="Element">Select Elements dialog-box</link> opens, you have clicked more than one <text styleclass="Element">Point</text>. </para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">You must select one <text styleclass="Element">Point</text>.</para>
                <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="lower-alpha" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Bulleted2" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted2">Click a <text styleclass="Element">Point</text> in the<text style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Interface">Select Elements dialog-box</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted2">Click <image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> to close the <text styleclass="Interface">Select Elements dialog-box</text>&#32;</li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">then...</para>
                <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text>&#32;<image src="OK-tiny-11-15.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> in the <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Command-Manager" styleclass="Interface">Command-Manager</link><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Bullets">The <text styleclass="Element">Trace-Point</text> is now in the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
